                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-800 to-blue-900"></div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-6xl opacity-30">ğŸ›¡ï¸</div>
                    <div class="relative p-6 text-center">
                        <div class="text-4xl mb-3">ğŸ”µ</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Default Blue</h3>
                        <p class="text-white/70 text-sm mb-4">Classic police theme with blue colors, standard cursor</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                            <span class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-blue-600"></span>
                            <span class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-blue-400"></span>
