                    <ul class="text-white/80 text-sm space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
                        <li>Live countdown timer to January 1, 2026 (CST)</li>
                        <li>Falling confetti animation (ğŸ‰ ğŸŠ ğŸ¥³ ğŸ‡ ğŸ† âœ¨ â­)</li>
